Articles.Content:
I do wonder about that too Varsi. From personal experience the game becomes generally less stable with lots of complex flights in progress. More so if those flights involve docking connections.

The most recent time I saw this however was vanilla(ish). I had KAC/KER/PNode only. The tractor/surface base that bugged out was aimed at a high-end contract on Duna surface and was the only craft outside Kerbin's SOI...but kerbin space was full with 30-odd surface/orbital stations and other misc craft.

@eddiew: Good plan, think i'll have to start a similar routinue.
